<p>
	This lovely deck of tarot cards is illustrated by Sergio Tisselli who creates a harmonic bond between the knowledge of tarot and the old wisdom of Native Americans. This Native American tarot deck combines the traditional way of tarot reading with the shamanism of the Native Americans, combining wisdom and strength with the harmony of nature. This fantastic deck of tarot cards comes with instructions and features 78 cards&nbsp;in the size of 64mm x 122mm.</p>
